10
00:01:13,840 --> 00:01:14,640
Don't go.

11
00:01:19,400 --> 00:01:20,239
- You...
- Xian Ge.

12
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:28,120
You are Wang Jialuo,
constable of Dagu County Yamen.

13
00:01:29,760 --> 00:01:30,799
What do you want to say?

14
00:01:35,920 --> 00:01:37,640
I'm investigating a murder case.

15
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:39,079
Chen Wu, who was just inside,

16
00:01:39,239 --> 00:01:40,480
