19
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:46,239
He died during the interrogation.

20
00:01:46,680 --> 00:01:47,879
You violated the Qing Code...

21
00:01:47,879 --> 00:01:50,000
The Qing Code made for the common people

22
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:52,120
