to conduct cases.

23
00:01:52,439 --> 00:01:53,120
But we never

24
00:01:53,120 --> 00:01:54,680
get restricted by the Code.

25
00:01:54,680 --> 00:01:55,599
Don't you know that?

26
00:01:55,879 --> 00:01:57,040
How dare a menial constable

27
00:01:57,040 --> 00:01:59,000
stand in our way?

28
00:01:59,319 --> 00:02:01,920
Going back to the gambling house now
and moving the corpse

29
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:05,400
