I heard you asking someone at the inn
about the gambling house,

35
00:02:41,159 --> 00:02:42,479
so I followed you here.

36
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:44,560
But I didn't dare to go inside.

37
00:02:46,039 --> 00:02:49,159
I just found a person,

38
00:02:49,680 --> 00:02:50,960
he should somehow

39
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,960
