46
00:03:14,759 --> 00:03:15,599
I'm going to Tianjin.

47
00:03:16,400 --> 00:03:18,080
I just heard that person mention

48
00:03:18,159 --> 00:03:19,400
a pawnshop in Tianjin.

49
00:03:19,680 --> 00:03:21,479
It should be related
to those people from Lingxi.

50
00:03:21,840 --> 00:03:23,560
I might find some clues there.

51
00:03:27,759 --> 00:03:29,319
I want to investigate the case with you.

52
00:03:29,719 --> 00:03:30,719
I want to know why they

53
