72
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:11,199
You are right, sir.

73
00:06:11,480 --> 00:06:12,160
But this...

74
00:06:12,279 --> 00:06:12,839
Whip.

75
00:06:12,839 --> 00:06:13,439
Whip?

76
00:06:14,560 --> 00:06:15,319
A soft whip.

77
00:06:26,759 --> 00:06:27,879
The bruise was not made by tools,

78
00:06:28,160 --> 00:06:29,240
