81
00:06:36,800 --> 00:06:38,920
They wanted to escape but failed.

82
00:06:39,120 --> 00:06:40,399
Throttling the jawbone and neck,

83
00:06:40,399 --> 00:06:41,759
was to coerce them for information.

84
00:06:42,160 --> 00:06:43,560
Judging from their bones and muscles,

85
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:45,399
these victims knew Kung Fu.

86
00:06:45,720 --> 00:06:46,959
The killer killed them all at once

87
00:06:47,279 --> 00:06:49,079
without alerting the other people
in the inn.

88
00:06:49,240 --> 00:06:51,839
That means this person
was not only skilled in using poison,

89
00:06:51,839 --> 00:06:53,439
but his Kung Fu was also exceptional.

90
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:55,839
Then sir, in your opinion,

91
00:06:55,839 --> 00:06:57,560
what poison was used on these people?

92
00:07:02,240 --> 00:07:03,519
Lingxi strange poison.

93
00:07:03,879 --> 00:07:05,160
Lingxi strange poison?

94
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:07,600
And the person
who took the pawn ticket from Chen Wu

95
00:07:07,600 --> 00:07:09,199
was also disguised
as someone from Lingxi.

96
00:07:10,439 --> 00:07:12,120
A martial arts master-hand from Lingxi.

97
00:07:13,319 --> 00:07:14,879
Is there any master from Lingxi?

98
00:07:15,639 --> 00:07:16,480
Zhuo Bufan.

99
00:07:17,199 --> 00:07:18,800
Zhuo Bufan,
the Sect Leader of Rongtian Ridge?

100
00:07:19,639 --> 00:07:21,800
He was already a grandmaster
over a decade ago.

101
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:23,759
His swordsmanship is unmatched.

102
00:07:24,399 --> 00:07:25,519
However,

103
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:28,319
Rongtian Ridge is in the far Lingxi.

104
00:07:29,079 --> 00:07:30,920
When Zhuo Bufan was young,

105
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:32,399
his swordsmanship was unparalleled.

106
00:07:32,399 --> 00:07:34,160
He was also an unruly and untamed man.

107
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:35,399
Why did he kill them

108
00:07:35,399 --> 00:07:37,519
without leaving his name?

109
00:07:38,399 --> 00:07:40,079
Moreover, as a wandering swordsman,

110
00:07:40,240 --> 00:07:42,480
how could he get involved in rebellion?

111
00:07:46,959 --> 00:07:49,680
(Prison of Imperial Household Department)
The dreamy wish has never come true.

112
00:07:49,680 --> 00:07:52,680
My talents are restricted to triviality
that I can't get rid of.

113
00:07:59,360 --> 00:08:02,600
Six years ago,
I knew that you served under Prince Qi.

114
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:05,279
I kept you because I had other plans.

115
00:08:05,839 --> 00:08:08,040
But now, you are not just hurting me,

116
00:08:08,959 --> 00:08:11,160
you are jeopardizing
the whole Qing Dynasty.

117
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:13,879
Rebellion is a serious crime.

118
00:08:14,120 --> 00:08:16,720
You and your entire clan
would be executed.

119
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:19,399
However, after all,

120
00:08:19,399 --> 00:08:21,439
you have followed me for ten years.

121
00:08:21,839 --> 00:08:24,000
I will give you one last chance.

122
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:27,680
As long as you are willing to confess,

123
00:08:28,680 --> 00:08:29,800
you will be the only one to die.

124
00:08:31,439 --> 00:08:34,080
The treasure map of Wenyuan Pavilion

125
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:37,320
is not complete.

126
00:08:37,679 --> 00:08:42,360
There is one person
who knows the secret of treasure map.

127
00:08:49,399 --> 00:08:50,000
Your Highness.

128
00:08:52,480 --> 00:08:53,919
Greetings, Your Highness.

129
00:08:54,919 --> 00:08:55,600
Your Highness.

130
00:08:56,039 --> 00:08:57,000
Congratulations.

131
00:08:57,200 --> 00:08:58,759
What is there to congratulate?

132
00:08:59,480 --> 00:09:02,039
I just took one step forward.

133
00:09:04,320 --> 00:09:04,879
Have a seat.

134
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,080
Please.

135
00:09:08,879 --> 00:09:10,360
It's more than what you said.

136
00:09:10,799 --> 00:09:13,840
The Department hasn't taken this step
in over 100 years.

137
00:09:14,360 --> 00:09:17,960
If you didn't tell me the whole story

138
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:19,120
of the Altar Treasure

139
00:09:19,559 --> 00:09:23,279
and that the treasure map
was hidden in Wenyuan Pavilion.

140
00:09:23,559 --> 00:09:25,919
How could I have had the chance
to obtain it?

141
00:09:26,759 --> 00:09:30,120
It is still too early to say that.

142
00:09:31,159 --> 00:09:32,360
Obtaining the treasure or not

143
00:09:32,879 --> 00:09:35,200
depends on Zhuo Bufan.

144
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:38,159
Now Zhuo Bufan already
has half of the treasure map.

145
00:09:38,279 --> 00:09:39,879
With his capability,

146
00:09:40,320 --> 00:09:42,799
I am sure he will get the other half.

147
00:09:43,519 --> 00:09:45,039
What do you think of Zhuo Bufan?

148
00:09:45,639 --> 00:09:48,240
A once-in-a-century genius swordsman.

149
00:09:49,639 --> 00:09:51,679
You praised his skills, but not him.

150
00:09:51,879 --> 00:09:53,279
What's your concern about him?

151
00:09:53,639 --> 00:09:54,919
Everyone is greedy.

152
00:09:55,120 --> 00:09:56,399
For such a great treasure,

153
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:59,200
I'm afraid they can't help themselves.

154
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,240
Yes.

155
00:10:02,360 --> 00:10:03,960
Such a huge treasure.

156
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:06,159
What's the harm
in sharing some with them?

157
00:10:06,720 --> 00:10:07,840
Your Highness,

158
00:10:07,840 --> 00:10:09,879
you must have
made a sweet deal with them.

159
00:10:10,519 --> 00:10:12,879
It is for him,

160
00:10:13,759 --> 00:10:14,799
but for me,

161
00:10:15,559 --> 00:10:16,519
it's just a useless title.

162
00:10:16,720 --> 00:10:18,399
Zhuo Bufan wanted a main altar

163
00:10:18,399 --> 00:10:21,440
and to be recognized
as the first Sword Sect.

164
00:10:21,759 --> 00:10:22,840
I said yes right away.

165
00:10:23,879 --> 00:10:25,279
The lord has written back.

166
00:10:25,879 --> 00:10:26,879
What did Prince Qi say?

167
00:10:27,720 --> 00:10:28,480
He said

168
00:10:29,120 --> 00:10:31,559
he was quite satisfied
with our current progress,

169
00:10:31,679 --> 00:10:33,600
but we must keep going.

170
00:10:35,799 --> 00:10:36,360
Okay.

171
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:38,639
Huanjie.

172
00:10:39,080 --> 00:10:40,559
We are handling this thing
for Prince Qi.

173
00:10:40,960 --> 00:10:43,720
Only you, I, and Ms. Huo know about it.

174
00:10:43,759 --> 00:10:44,759
I know.

175
00:10:45,000 --> 00:10:46,919
I'm not telling the other disciples

176
00:10:47,559 --> 00:10:48,759
because I want to keep it simple,

177
00:10:48,759 --> 00:10:50,080
and don't want them to be panic.

178
00:10:50,519 --> 00:10:52,240
I hope you can keep this secret for me.

179
00:10:53,879 --> 00:10:54,639
Bufan.

180
00:10:55,559 --> 00:10:56,480
After all,

181
00:10:56,879 --> 00:10:59,080
I am also a senior
of Rongtian Sword Sect.

182
00:10:59,840 --> 00:11:02,879
Of course, I will keep this a secret.

183
00:11:03,519 --> 00:11:04,480
Rest assured.

184
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:07,360
Huanjie.

185
00:11:10,879 --> 00:11:12,159
Just as we discussed yesterday,

186
00:11:12,399 --> 00:11:14,279
Huanjie,
you take the waterway to Shanghai first.

187
00:11:14,759 --> 00:11:15,320
Tang Yu.

188
00:11:15,480 --> 00:11:17,360
Remember to prepare the clothes
for your meet-up.

189
00:11:17,399 --> 00:11:20,200
We'll walk through Linqing and Huai'an
to reach Shanghai.

190
00:11:20,399 --> 00:11:22,200
Leave the others to Qin Tuo.

191
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:23,480
Mr. Zhuo.

192
00:11:26,720 --> 00:11:27,519
Everyone, take care.

193
00:11:28,600 --> 00:11:30,279
There are many highly-skilled swordsmen.

194
00:11:30,360 --> 00:11:32,639
Why chose the desolate Rongtian Ridge?

195
00:11:32,759 --> 00:11:33,360
Kneel down.

196
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:33,919
Kneel.

197
00:11:33,919 --> 00:11:35,120
Why should I kneel? I...

198
00:11:35,360 --> 00:11:36,600
Kneel down.

199
00:11:36,919 --> 00:11:37,919
What are you doing?

200
00:11:38,120 --> 00:11:40,399
I don't trust those
famous martial arts masters.

201
00:11:40,759 --> 00:11:42,080
Zhuo Bufan is different.

202
00:11:42,480 --> 00:11:44,440
He's a very proud man.

203
00:11:44,879 --> 00:11:46,799
If it weren't for utter destitution,

204
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:50,960
he would never deign
to serve the powerful.

205
00:11:51,639 --> 00:11:54,279
Perhaps some people

206
00:11:54,639 --> 00:11:57,240
think serving me is an honor.

207
00:11:57,240 --> 00:11:58,799
But for him,

208
00:11:59,519 --> 00:12:00,639
it is a disgrace.

209
00:12:01,080 --> 00:12:02,519
Rongtian Ridge

210
00:12:02,519 --> 00:12:04,559
is the epitome
of poverty and desolation.

211
00:12:04,879 --> 00:12:08,279
Even someone ambitious like Zhuo Bufan

212
00:12:08,480 --> 00:12:10,639
cannot withstand the poverty.

213
00:12:13,559 --> 00:12:16,320
Yielding once to change his future.

214
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:18,360
He knows what really matters.

215
00:12:37,200 --> 00:12:38,320
Do you think

216
00:12:38,720 --> 00:12:40,120
I'm a burden to you?

217
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:44,039
If I think so,

218
00:12:44,360 --> 00:12:45,960
why don't I just be alone?

219
00:12:47,320 --> 00:12:49,360
You and other disciples

220
00:12:49,759 --> 00:12:50,960
are all my burdens.

221
00:12:54,279 --> 00:12:55,200
You must remember,

222
00:12:55,759 --> 00:12:57,039
Our Sword Sect is a sect.

223
00:12:57,320 --> 00:12:58,960
Sword Sect exists
because of every one of you.

224
00:13:03,960 --> 00:13:05,679
Alright, go pack.

225
00:13:06,000 --> 00:13:06,919
We must set off now.

226
00:13:19,039 --> 00:13:19,720
Huanjie.

227
00:13:20,759 --> 00:13:24,000
You are the one
who taught me basic sword moves.

228
00:13:26,440 --> 00:13:27,720
Whip techniques suit you better.

229
00:13:28,480 --> 00:13:30,200
The master
made the right choice for you.

230
00:13:31,480 --> 00:13:33,279
But I still prefer the sword.

231
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:37,399
Now is not the time

232
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:39,200
to do what you like.

233
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:43,000
Okay.

234
00:13:58,320 --> 00:14:00,320
We still didn't find the Altar Treasure.

235
00:14:00,320 --> 00:14:01,759
We have looked everywhere.

236
00:14:02,960 --> 00:14:04,279
But there is one person who knows

237
00:14:04,279 --> 00:14:05,600
the secret of the treasure map.

238
00:14:06,519 --> 00:14:08,879
And Prince Qi already knows about this.

239
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:11,519
This person was a supporter
of the Reform Movement of 1898.

240
00:14:11,679 --> 00:14:14,080
And he fled to overseas
after Wuxu Reform.

241
00:14:14,360 --> 00:14:17,000
He wants to offer this secret
to the Tongmenghui.

242
00:14:18,159 --> 00:14:19,480
His name is Tan Xian.

243
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:21,480
And he will return to the country soon.

244
00:14:21,639 --> 00:14:23,360
