245
00:14:23,799 --> 00:14:25,480
Once he controls Tan Xian,

246
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:26,919
he will have in control

247
00:14:26,919 --> 00:14:28,440
all the secrets about the treasure.

248
00:14:29,039 --> 00:14:30,519
